after seeing your face.

82
00:06:56,253 --> 00:06:58,421
"Do you regret
killing your wife and children?"

83
00:07:00,090 --> 00:07:02,884
"Have you repented at all?"

84
00:07:08,890 --> 00:07:10,308
"Have you been forgiven?"

85
00:07:12,477 --> 00:07:14,771
