695
00:49:16,501 --> 00:49:18,003
Secretly tracking down

696
00:49:18,128 --> 00:49:21,756
pathetic demons who've become humanized
or fallen in love like you.

697
00:49:23,091 --> 00:49:24,259
That's my mission.

698
00:49:28,597 --> 00:49:29,723
