-[bystander 2] Call 911!

713
00:50:32,786 --> 00:50:33,954
[bystander 3] Oh, my goodness!

714
00:50:34,037 --> 00:50:36,164
-[bystander 1] Please hurry!
-[bystander 2] Oh, no!

715
